{"tid":875125,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[HK No IT] 科技人才139配額獲批主要來自內地　月薪最高8萬","createTime":"2018-10-24T16:36:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-25T09:43:32.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"343158a6fb182039b40b089114fcf716d12d661c","tid":875125,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T16:36:05.000Z","msg":"創新及科技局今年5月推出「科技人才入境計劃」，至本月收到156個申請，創新科技署已批出139個配額予19間科技公司或機構，<span style=\"color: red;\">當中獲批的人才主要來自內地</span>，月薪2萬港元以上，以從事數據分析的最多。<br />\n<br />\n該局表示，向科技公司或機構最常發放約5個人才配額，個別公司獲批配額數目達11至20個以上。<span style=\"color: red;\">業務範疇以數據分析為主</span>，有公司獲發6個人才配額，其次是人工智能及金融科技，各有5個配額。<br />\n<br />\n入境事務處就相關申請已批出12個工作簽證或進入許可，獲准入境人才中，內地佔7個，其次來自亞洲及澳洲，分別有4個及1個。有3名人才的月薪高達8萬港元以上，6人月薪介乎4萬至8萬港元，另有3人月薪2萬至4萬港元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181024/bkn-20181024152935409-1024_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181024%2Fbkn-20181024152935409-1024_00822_001.html&d=m29a5ld8Zh9M1evcMgLd2zANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=4b2b3264\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181024/bkn-20181024152935409-1024_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"afc3fcd770eacb4a77d68aa81e5a65e1c63d1944","tid":875125,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T16:36:37.000Z","msg":"業務範疇以數據分析為主<br />\n業務範疇以數據分析為主<br />\n業務範疇以數據分析為主<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbe2c89d20c4d431777db2a0f3d37fd10a3d5e33","tid":875125,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T04:13:42.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"b6583e06d0f73b6c2a087ddc014ed3f6ba712536","tid":875125,"uid":19454,